        "body": "Fix endless indentation of multi-line HTML comments in markdown lists (#18066)\r\n\r\n**Description**\r\nMulti-line HTML comments in list items were getting additional indentation on each format. Fixed by changing the regex from `/^<!--.*-->$/su to /^<!--.*-->$/u` (removed s flag) so multi-line comments use [markAsRoot(literalline)](https://obscure-eureka-4jww4v7x4j4j2j99g.github.dev/) like other HTML, preserving original formatting.\r\n\r\nFixes #18066\r\n\r\n**Checklist**\r\n\r\n- [x]  I've added tests to confirm my change works.\r\n- [x]  I've added my changes to [18066.md](https://obscure-eureka-4jww4v7x4j4j2j99g.github.dev/).\r\n- [x]  I've read the contributing guidelines.",
